    Package Description
    ch.ecma.csta.callassociated
    Provides the services for performing high-level third party call associated functions.
    ch.ecma.csta.callcontrol
    Provides the services, listener, and adapter for performing high-level third party call control.
    ch.ecma.csta.capabilityexchange  
    ch.ecma.csta.errors
    This package contains classes that directly map to the CSTA Diagnostic Error Definitions.
    ch.ecma.csta.logical
    Provide the services, listener, and adapter for performing logical device feature services and events.
    ch.ecma.csta.media
    Not supported.
    ch.ecma.csta.monitor
    Contains classes for removing and adding listeners.
    ch.ecma.csta.physical
    Contains classes for monitoring and controlling the physical aspects of a device.
    ch.ecma.csta.routeing  
    ch.ecma.csta.snapshot
    Provides the SnapshotCall and SnapshotDevice services.
    ch.ecma.csta.system
    Not supported.
    ch.ecma.csta.voiceunit
    Contains classes for recording and playing voice messages.
    com.avaya.cmapi
    Contains ServiceProvider class which is the starting point to obtain access to any of the services provided in this API.
    com.avaya.cmapi.callinformation
    Provides the services, listener, and adapter that allow applications to query for call details on a given device.
    com.avaya.csta.async
    Allows clients to receive responses to requests asynchronously.
    com.avaya.csta.device
    Contains DeviceServices class for obtaining and releasing device IDs that represent a particular device.
    com.avaya.csta.e164
    Provides services to convert from E.164 to a switch dial string (extension, for example) and vice-versa.
    com.avaya.csta.errors  
    com.avaya.csta.media
    Not supported.
    com.avaya.csta.monitor  
    com.avaya.csta.registration
    Contains classes for gaining exclusive or shared control over Communication Manager phones/extensions and their media streams.
    com.avaya.csta.terminal
    Contains classes for gaining exclusive or shared control over Communication Manager phones/extensions and their media streams.
    com.avaya.csta.tonecollection
    Contains classes for collecting and reporting multiple DTMF tones received on a device.
    com.avaya.csta.tonedetection
    Contains classes for detecting and reporting individual DTMF tones received on a device.
    com.avaya.csta.voiceunit
    Contains classes that extend CSTA Voice Unit Services, such as dubbing a recording and suspending/resuming/stopping either the player or the recorder.
